the recent meme-stock aftershock =E2=80=94=C2=A0in which the X account of K=
eith Gill, the famous GameStop bull known as Roaring Kitty, tweeted some st=
uff that caused the stock to rally =E2=80=94=C2=A0involves this sort of ret=
ail leverage. Gill tweeted, everyone online was like =E2=80=9Ccool we=E2=80=
