<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One such Tesla investor-influencer is Yaman Ta=
sdivar (37,600 followers on X), who has hosted regular meetups on Spaces, t=
he audio chatroom function on X, where participants debate questions such a=
