other deeper into the fear that their Tesla investments are at risk. Anothe=
r is Sawyer Merritt (683,900 followers on X) who posts incremental Tesla ne=
ws multiple times a day and who garnered a repost from Musk in early May wi=
th detailed instructions on how to vote.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[=E2=80=9CTeslaBoomerMama X poster Alexandra] =
Merz, a 58-year-old mother of five and owner of a business consulting firm,=
