<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A fun thesis is =E2=80=9Cthe rise of GLP-1 ago=
nist medications for obesity will lead to crashing global demand for sugar,=
 so you should short sugar futures.=E2=80=9D It=E2=80=99s a great story abo=
ut how the world works: Changing consumer preferences lead to changing dema=
nd for commodities, and if the consumer preferences are changed=C2=A0<em>by=
 a drug</em>, then (1) that will have an effect on commodity prices and (2)=
 that=E2=80=99s cool and weird.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand it=E2=80=99s probably not=C2=
=A0<em>true</em>? Or maybe you can tell a story where in 50 years half of t=
he world is on GLP-1 drugs and nobody eats sugar, but that is, you know, a =
lot of sugar crops from now. Here is a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/35536316.258326/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZX=
dzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDUtMjgvd2VpZ2h0LWxvc3MtZHJ1Z3MtYXJlLWNvbWluZy10by1ia=
XRlLWEtc3VnYXItaW5kdXN0cnktaW4tZGVuaWFsP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA1MjkyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZG=
