ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
very fun story</a> about how sugar traders have absolutely no interest in t=
his thesis, but it=E2=80=99s so cool that people want to talk about it even=
 though they end each sentence by muttering =E2=80=9C=E2=80=A6=C2=A0in 2035=
=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In a room filled with more than 800 sugar trad=
ers, Sally Lyons Wyatt, an executive at consumer researcher Circana, had an=
 important message to deliver: Ozempic is coming for your industry.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDoes it have the ability to be huge i=
n the future?=E2=80=9D she asked during her speech at the New York Sugar Di=
nner earlier this month. =E2=80=9CIt does.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Nobody appeared to be paying attention. =E2=80=
=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Sugar traders, used to seeing demand grow as p=
opulation expands, could be overlooking the next big demand hit. The drugs,=
 which cut cravings, will result in a decline in calorie consumption in the=
 US of 1.5% to 2.5% by 2035, with a drop of as much as 5% in the consumptio=
n of sweets such as baked goods, confectionery and soda, Morgan Stanley ana=
lysts including Pamela Kaufman said in a report last month. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m spending a lot of time th=
inking about it because I think it could be really important,=E2=80=9D said=
 Stephen Geldart, the head of analysis at London-based commodities trader C=
zarnikow Group Ltd. =E2=80=9CMaybe I=E2=80=99m wrong, but if no one else is=
 paying any attention, that=E2=80=99s great. I=E2=80=99m quite happy to do =
things that no one else is looking at.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Further down, people boringly say =E2=80=9Cno =
obviously this is not an important factor come on=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Carlos Murilo Barros de Mello, the head of sug=
ar in the Americas at brokerage Hedgepoint Global Markets, said the industr=
y hasn=E2=80=99t spent significant time estimating consumption because shif=
ts are =E2=80=9Cminuscule=E2=80=9D relative to production swings.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The impact hasn=E2=80=99t been felt yet as =E2=
=80=9Cit=E2=80=99s still very much further down the line,=E2=80=9D said Kon=
a Haque, head of research at ED&amp;F Man. =E2=80=9CAnd don=E2=80=99t forge=
t, this is still very much an advanced-economy, affluent-society syndrome w=
here people are trying to tackle obesity.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Haque stressed that sugar demand is still grow=
ing in emerging markets, where the medications aren=E2=80=99t yet being mar=
keted.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But one day!</p>
