index, because the name started with =E2=80=9CGreen,=E2=80=9D though it deg=
enerated from there to =E2=80=9CPipelines.=E2=80=9D There will be=C2=A0<em>=
some=C2=A0</em>people (1)=C2=A0who want to avoid companies allegedly affili=
ated with the Chinese military but (2) whose due diligence will consist of=
=C2=A0<em>looking at the name</em>. So you might as well put =E2=80=9CAmeri=
can=E2=80=9D in the name.</p>
