ate events</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Kelley James ...=C2=A0is a singer and performe=
r whom companies hire for corporate events. He is best known for improvisin=
g songs that poke fun at the personal quirks and weak golf games of CEOs an=
d other powerful people. He=E2=80=99s ribbed the likes of Tiger Woods and S=
tephen Curry at golf tournaments, and rapped about fossil fuels for Saudi e=
xecutives. His highly researched needling earns him hundreds of thousands o=
f dollars a night.=C2=A0=E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When Delta Air Lines hired him to perform at a=
 party for clients at the Masters golf tournament last year, he did a frees=
tyle rap riffing on CEO Ed Bastian=E2=80=99s tendency to fly economy and si=
t in the rear of the aircraft=E2=80=94unlike his 9-pound terrier, Oliver. =
=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CEd=E2=80=99s in back of the plane, we=
 know it=E2=80=99s tradition, a man of the people, not many leaders like hi=
m, walking through TSA, shaking hands with the pilots, all while his dog go=
es on vacation and only flies private!=E2=80=9D James sang.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oliver, who recently died at 19 years old, did=
n=E2=80=99t actually fly private, though he did sometimes join Bastian=E2=
=80=99s wife in first class. Bastian loved the bit.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI don=E2=80=99t know if I ever laughe=
d so hard in my life,=E2=80=9D he says.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIf you want to make fun of my legenda=
ry love of cashews, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/clic=
