kground-color: #ccc;">you have at it</a>.=E2=80=9D There=E2=80=99s another =
anecdote about James roasting Egon Durban for his =E2=80=9Chabit of using c=
ryptic shorthand while sending text messages, which his employees live in f=
ear of misinterpreting=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CWhen the Egon text hits t=
he phone you immediately read, praying he=E2=80=99ll use the English langua=
ge but all that you see is a handful of gibberish typed by a toddler in mit=
tens,=E2=80=9D James sang.=C2=A0=E2=80=9CIf you respond wrong, better have =
your resignation written.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I bet he gets a lot of mileage out of those ba=
rs. Put any two-syllable executive name in there for =E2=80=9CEgon=E2=80=9D=
 and all the employees at the offsite will be like =E2=80=9Cooh got him, he=
 really nailed his brusque texting habit.=E2=80=9D He had =E2=80=9Cnearly $=
10 million in revenue=E2=80=9D in 2023 from 112 shows.</p>
